From 7d1a2d9c34d0a36af7fd760745d2f86a1bee32f7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Faisal Khan <mfkhan@sofi.org>
Date: Wed, 1 Apr 2026 17:13:25 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Enhance SEO and accessibility features across the
 application

- Updated angular.json to include additional assets for improved site functionality.
- Enhanced nginx.conf with security headers and caching strategies for better performance.
- Modified index.html to include Open Graph and Twitter Card metadata for improved social sharing.
- Implemented skip link for better accessibility in shell.component.html.
- Refactored blog post component to dynamically update meta tags based on content.
- Improved blog service to return observable for post loading, enhancing data handling.
- Updated styles for project cards to improve text visibility and user experience.
